  "prompt": "How many grafts are needed to get a full beard by facial hair transplant? How much will it cost in India?",
  "response": "The number of grafts required for a full beard transplant can vary depending on the individual's facial hair density, the desired beard style, and the thickness of the hair. On average, a full beard transplant may require anywhere from 2,500 to 3,500 grafts.\n\nThe cost of a beard transplant in India can vary based on several factors, including the clinic, the expertise of the surgeon, the location, and the number of grafts required. Generally, the cost per graft in India can range from INR 20 to INR 100. Therefore, the total cost for a full beard transplant can range from INR 50,000 to INR 3,50,000.\n\nIt is important to consult with a qualified and experienced surgeon to get a personalized assessment and accurate cost estimate based on your specific needs.",
